ABC bank offers services to its various customers. 
The bank has various branches all over the country and 
therefore each of the branches has a unique id. 
The bank stores the details of its customers, 
such as customer name, account number, address, phone number, and e-mail address. In addition, 
the bank stores the various details of its employees, 
such as employee name, employee id, address, phone number, and e-mail id. 
The bank offers its customers a choice of accounts, such as savings, and current account. 
Identify the various classes and their attributes. Upload the code.

----------------------------------------------------

Branch
id,location,managerID (employee_ID), bank_name(constant)

Person
name,id,address,phone number,email address, type (customer/employee)

Customer extends person
Employee extends person

CustomerAccountDetails

customerID,account number, account type(Savings,current account)
current Balance